WEBVTT

01:36.970 --> 01:40.950
[The Best Thing]

01:41.450 --> 01:48.440
[Episode 11: Dragon bones are astringent and sweet in taste and neutral in nature. They calm the mind, pacify the liver, subdue yang, and stabilize bodily functions.]

01:57.410 --> 01:58.210
Do you eat pepper?

02:09.240 --> 02:10.030
Dr. He.

02:15.840 --> 02:16.710
What's this?

02:28.730 --> 02:29.930
This keychain…

02:30.190 --> 02:30.860
I...

02:31.829 --> 02:33.000
What's this?

02:33.020 --> 02:33.840
The white item.

02:37.590 --> 02:38.630
It's a dragon bone.

02:39.000 --> 02:39.840
Dragon bone?

02:40.390 --> 02:41.360
Like an actual dragon's bone?

02:41.750 --> 02:43.030
Not a real dragon's bone.

02:44.040 --> 02:45.670
In TCM,

02:45.710 --> 02:47.710
ancient mammal fossils are referred to

02:47.710 --> 02:48.840
as dragon bones.

02:49.210 --> 02:49.880
Look,

02:50.520 --> 02:52.430
this piece is from a joint,

02:52.430 --> 02:54.490
so it has all these honeycomb-like holes.

02:54.510 --> 02:55.630
It can be used as a keychain.

02:59.240 --> 02:59.960
Dr. He.

03:01.140 --> 03:03.180
Isn't it illegal for you to possess a fossil?

03:04.130 --> 03:05.740
This isn't a real fossil.

03:05.770 --> 03:07.530
How could I possibly buy a real one?

03:08.480 --> 03:10.510
It's just a cow bone buried underground by farmers.

03:10.580 --> 03:11.300
It's also used as medicine.

03:11.910 --> 03:12.820
It calms the liver, subdues yang,

03:12.840 --> 03:13.770
soothes the mind, and promotes blood circulation.

03:17.630 --> 03:18.400
Alright.

03:18.510 --> 03:19.480
Go wash your hands for dinner.

03:19.510 --> 03:20.190
It's almost ready.

03:21.000 --> 03:21.800
Restroom's to the left.

03:47.240 --> 03:48.560
What's wrong? Does it taste bad?

03:49.130 --> 03:50.360
No, it's delicious.

03:51.420 --> 03:52.400
Let me get you a bowl of soup.

03:53.190 --> 03:53.870
Thank you.

03:54.030 --> 03:54.590
Give me your bowl.

04:03.370 --> 04:04.350
Oh, Dr. He,

04:04.590 --> 04:05.750
did you see the group photo

04:05.750 --> 04:06.750
I sent you?

04:06.770 --> 04:07.820
Let me show you again.

04:08.070 --> 04:08.740
Okay.

04:11.460 --> 04:12.150
Here.

04:29.700 --> 04:30.700
What's wrong?

04:32.360 --> 04:33.430
This photo...

04:34.430 --> 04:35.360
is not very good.

04:35.730 --> 04:36.730
Not very good?

04:37.800 --> 04:40.120
But I think you look quite handsome in it.

04:40.190 --> 04:41.000
What don't you like about it?

04:41.000 --> 04:41.730
I can edit it for you.

04:42.270 --> 04:43.240
It's not about editing.

04:44.750 --> 04:45.960
I look too serious.

04:47.890 --> 04:50.210
Looking serious is good.

04:50.240 --> 04:52.090
It shows that our consultant

04:52.120 --> 04:53.040
is dedicated

04:53.040 --> 04:54.159
and professional.

04:54.430 --> 04:57.260
I mean, I look so serious

04:57.260 --> 04:59.310
that it doesn't reflect my mood that day.

05:02.020 --> 05:02.750
Mood?

05:04.340 --> 05:05.580
That day…

05:06.510 --> 05:07.630
I was really happy.

05:27.260 --> 05:28.140
It's hot.

05:32.700 --> 05:33.350
Here.

05:35.220 --> 05:35.990
Thank you.

05:56.630 --> 05:57.380
Dr. He,

05:57.820 --> 06:00.460
my parents just messaged me, asking me to go home.

06:00.460 --> 06:01.900
I'll be leaving now.

06:05.700 --> 06:07.260
Well, wait for me a moment.

06:07.290 --> 06:08.900
I need to take the trash downstairs.

06:08.920 --> 06:09.710
Let's go down together.

06:09.830 --> 06:10.420
Okay.

06:26.020 --> 06:28.070
Well, I'm heading home.

06:31.700 --> 06:32.340
Okay.

06:33.220 --> 06:33.630
Bye-bye.

06:34.190 --> 06:34.780
Bye-bye.

07:11.260 --> 07:12.110
Dr. He,

07:12.510 --> 07:13.380
look at this.

07:13.810 --> 07:14.930
Doesn't it look like a ring?

07:16.580 --> 07:18.630
Keep it. No need to thank me.

07:18.950 --> 07:20.680
The thing you gave me at noon…

07:21.040 --> 07:22.120
I lost it.

07:22.590 --> 07:24.380
It was gone when I got off work.

07:25.380 --> 07:26.190
Dr. He.

07:28.720 --> 07:30.160
What is this?

07:45.100 --> 07:47.490
It wasn't the same ring, was it?

08:24.570 --> 08:25.770
Manager Shen,

08:25.800 --> 08:26.240
are you there?

08:27.910 --> 08:29.230
Received. I'm here.

08:30.110 --> 08:32.610
The guest in Room 8252 isn't feeling well,

08:32.640 --> 08:34.280
but she refuses to go to the hospital.

08:34.299 --> 08:35.510
Come check on her quickly.

08:35.789 --> 08:37.030
Alright, I'm on my way.

08:49.070 --> 08:49.860
Thank you.

08:51.550 --> 08:52.220
Manager,

08:52.400 --> 08:53.680
should we call an ambulance?

08:54.220 --> 08:55.030
That's not necessary.

08:55.580 --> 08:57.860
But what if something happens?

08:58.700 --> 09:00.070
I'm just in a bit of pain.

09:00.070 --> 09:01.400
I'll be fine after taking some medicine.

09:01.550 --> 09:02.790
Thank you both.

09:03.850 --> 09:05.610
How about this? You go back.

09:05.640 --> 09:06.830
I'll call you if anything comes up.

09:06.860 --> 09:07.310
Okay.

09:17.500 --> 09:18.990
Senior Lin,

09:19.070 --> 09:21.070
Room 8252 might need medical assistance.

09:22.050 --> 09:23.570
Should I call an ambulance?

09:27.170 --> 09:28.170
Keep it on standby for now.

09:28.220 --> 09:29.700
I'll let you know if she needs it.

09:30.110 --> 09:30.750
Alright.

09:31.170 --> 09:32.010
Okay.

09:43.580 --> 09:45.070
Thank you for today.

09:45.580 --> 09:47.310
I ran out of painkillers

09:47.310 --> 09:48.580
and didn't have time to buy more.

09:49.460 --> 09:50.390
It's okay.

09:51.070 --> 09:51.950
But…

09:52.310 --> 09:54.030
where does it hurt exactly?

09:54.340 --> 09:56.150
We work with a medical team

09:56.150 --> 09:57.590
that can offer you a free consultation.

09:57.620 --> 09:58.470
No need.

09:58.550 --> 10:00.070
This happens to me occasionally.

10:00.190 --> 10:02.070
Once I take painkillers, I'll be fine.

10:04.070 --> 10:04.910
I've noticed

10:05.140 --> 10:07.170
you don't hang out with your tour group much.

10:07.820 --> 10:10.190
I don't have the energy or stamina

10:10.580 --> 10:12.030
to wander around

10:12.030 --> 10:14.220
like the others.

10:14.860 --> 10:15.980
Besides,

10:15.980 --> 10:18.150
I'm not really familiar with them.

10:18.790 --> 10:19.390
Didn't you

10:19.770 --> 10:21.930
sign up for the trip with them?

10:21.980 --> 10:23.980
While traveling in another city,

10:23.980 --> 10:25.580
I learned about this tour group

10:25.580 --> 10:27.100
and just decided to join.

10:27.680 --> 10:29.680
I've been traveling like this for over a year.

10:30.350 --> 10:31.540
It's quite freeing.

10:34.690 --> 10:36.050
Hope you don't mind me asking—

10:36.510 --> 10:37.600
where's your family?

10:38.150 --> 10:39.390
My husband passed away.

10:40.670 --> 10:41.910
And my children

10:41.910 --> 10:43.150
are all abroad,

10:43.150 --> 10:44.740
too busy to take care of me.

10:45.430 --> 10:48.500
While I still have the energy,

10:48.500 --> 10:50.620
I want to see the beautiful landscapes of my country.

10:51.150 --> 10:52.430
So I sold my house

10:53.550 --> 10:54.670
and started traveling

10:54.910 --> 10:56.030
all around the country.

10:57.220 --> 11:00.620
I send them photos now and then

11:00.620 --> 11:02.020
to let them know I'm alright.

11:05.500 --> 11:07.910
Thank you so much for today, dear.

11:08.350 --> 11:10.310
Not at all. This is part of my job.

11:36.840 --> 11:39.360
I packed some freshly made soup for you.

11:39.740 --> 11:40.580
Thank you.

11:40.580 --> 11:42.150
Take it home for your parents.

11:42.150 --> 11:42.790
Okay.

11:44.190 --> 11:46.860
The medicinal cuisine combo was a huge success.

11:46.860 --> 11:48.150
We gained 10,000 followers on Weibo.

11:48.150 --> 11:48.860
Really?

11:48.860 --> 11:49.580
That many?

11:50.150 --> 11:51.030
Look for yourself.

11:52.460 --> 11:53.670
Amazing!

11:54.350 --> 11:56.620
I'm the biggest contributor here.

11:56.650 --> 11:59.170
This whole TCM wellness plan was my idea.

12:00.620 --> 12:03.500
Once this is over, I'll treat you to a fancy meal and a spa.

12:03.520 --> 12:04.190
Deal.

12:16.220 --> 12:16.950
Xiangya,

12:17.480 --> 12:20.030
you're not really interested in Li Jie, are you?

12:22.620 --> 12:25.150
Who doesn't like a cute young boy?

12:29.090 --> 12:30.250
I'm serious.

12:30.550 --> 12:32.980
What's going on between you and Senior Lin?

12:34.980 --> 12:36.570
You know he's going back to his hometown, right?

12:41.820 --> 12:43.310
If he's going back to start a family and build a career,

12:43.310 --> 12:44.430
I can't stop him.

12:45.910 --> 12:46.950
Well,

12:47.670 --> 12:49.310
maybe he hasn't made up his mind yet.

13:10.620 --> 13:11.310
Yeah,

13:12.460 --> 13:13.860
maybe he hasn't,

13:14.820 --> 13:16.980
but I'm not going to put my life on hold for his "maybe."

13:21.550 --> 13:23.500
You've only been in one relationship.

13:23.500 --> 13:24.980
You can't even figure out your own love life,

13:24.980 --> 13:26.070
yet you're giving me advice?

13:26.550 --> 13:28.550
Don't be so harsh.

13:29.310 --> 13:30.950
But seriously,

13:31.430 --> 13:33.220
go easy on Li Jie.

13:33.250 --> 13:34.890
He's been in school all this time.

13:34.910 --> 13:35.880
Don't mess with the poor boy.

13:37.080 --> 13:39.220
I told you, stay out of it.

13:39.220 --> 13:40.980
Can't you tell I'm not into him?

13:41.950 --> 13:42.550
He is

13:42.550 --> 13:44.830
a little goofy and kind of adorable.

13:44.920 --> 13:46.400
But I don't like him like that.

13:47.310 --> 13:49.210
That's what I thought.

13:49.310 --> 13:51.470
Your taste changed way too fast.

13:51.500 --> 13:53.860
You went from spicy hotpot to bland soup.

13:54.700 --> 13:55.780
Spot on.

13:56.460 --> 13:58.430
But don't tell Lin Yishen about it.

13:59.320 --> 14:00.200
Why?

14:00.500 --> 14:01.810
You're playing hard to get?

14:02.550 --> 14:03.340
It's not like that.

14:06.020 --> 14:07.100
I just think…

14:08.460 --> 14:11.030
there must be a reason why the stars have never aligned

14:12.740 --> 14:14.030
for us all these years.

14:15.430 --> 14:16.860
From college until now,

14:17.950 --> 14:19.500
when I was in a relationship, he was single;

14:19.870 --> 14:21.660
when I was single, he was in a relationship.

14:23.270 --> 14:23.950
I admit,

14:23.950 --> 14:25.670
I've dated a lot of guys,

14:25.670 --> 14:26.340
but

14:26.820 --> 14:27.580
if two people…

14:30.310 --> 14:31.700
keep missing the opportunities to be together,

14:32.070 --> 14:33.830
is it possible that they just

14:33.850 --> 14:35.130
don't like each other enough?

14:40.620 --> 14:41.270
Alright.

14:42.100 --> 14:43.500
Let's not talk about this anymore.

14:44.550 --> 14:46.450
We'll solve our problems ourselves.

14:47.980 --> 14:49.170
And your problems—

14:49.190 --> 14:50.880
you need to figure them out on your own too.

14:52.220 --> 14:52.790
I'm leaving.

15:22.370 --> 15:23.610
Here it is.

15:23.640 --> 15:24.400
What's it?

15:27.190 --> 15:28.860
Try the medicinal dish from the grand hotel.

15:29.550 --> 15:30.650
Let me see what's in it.

15:31.760 --> 15:34.710
Red dates, goji berries, pork ribs,

15:34.740 --> 15:35.820
taro,

15:36.700 --> 15:38.650
and… What's that small thing?

15:39.160 --> 15:41.640
That should be the Codonopsis root.

15:42.050 --> 15:42.970
Yep, that's right.

15:46.710 --> 15:47.420
Wait, wait!

15:47.450 --> 15:48.500
I need to take a photo first.

15:48.820 --> 15:50.270
I'll share it in the group chat

15:50.420 --> 15:53.260
so everyone can learn how to make this medicinal dish.

15:53.710 --> 15:54.350
Okay.

15:54.380 --> 15:55.220
Done?

15:58.100 --> 15:59.340
It smells amazing.

15:59.340 --> 16:00.290
By the way, Mom and Dad,

16:00.450 --> 16:02.290
you guys get annual health checkups, right?

16:02.340 --> 16:03.190
Of course.

16:03.750 --> 16:05.580
Are they comprehensive?

16:05.600 --> 16:06.490
Is anything wrong?

16:06.510 --> 16:07.420
Everything's fine.

16:07.650 --> 16:09.050
Your mom and I are very healthy.

16:10.610 --> 16:12.400
Why are you suddenly asking about this?

16:12.460 --> 16:14.620
I just realized

16:14.620 --> 16:15.910
I've never really paid attention

16:15.910 --> 16:17.310
to your health before.

16:19.970 --> 16:21.100
Finally having a conscience.

16:23.130 --> 16:25.090
We'll take good care of ourselves.

16:25.120 --> 16:26.280
You don't need to worry.

16:29.860 --> 16:30.620
I got a reply.

16:30.850 --> 16:33.330
They said this medicinal dish looks great…

16:36.670 --> 16:38.500
And that it was made by Li,

16:38.500 --> 16:40.190
the guy I set you up with on a blind date.

16:40.430 --> 16:41.860
They also said his mentor

16:41.860 --> 16:44.510
went to your hotel as a consultant with him.

16:44.590 --> 16:45.110
Really?

16:45.510 --> 16:46.390
Is that true?

16:50.340 --> 16:53.210
We invited him and his senior to be consultants.

16:53.390 --> 16:54.730
His senior brought him along.

16:56.680 --> 16:58.130
Then why don't you reach out to him directly?

16:58.580 --> 16:59.860
Why go in such a roundabout way?

16:59.860 --> 17:01.100
It's not like you don't know him.

17:01.100 --> 17:01.820
Just contact him directly.

17:03.270 --> 17:05.390
Why would I contact him?

17:05.390 --> 17:06.500
Didn't I already say it last time?

17:06.500 --> 17:08.020
I don't have feelings for him.

17:08.020 --> 17:08.950
Yeah, yeah,

17:09.300 --> 17:10.650
that same line again.

17:10.970 --> 17:12.260
You're brushing me off again.

17:13.670 --> 17:14.950
Every time I set you up on a blind date,

17:15.150 --> 17:16.430
you come back saying the exact same thing—

17:16.430 --> 17:17.589
"no feelings."

17:17.589 --> 17:18.430
You're just like your dad,

17:18.430 --> 17:19.460
always brushing me off.

17:21.220 --> 17:22.349
Why am I suddenly involved in this?

17:22.349 --> 17:23.950
When did I ever brush you off?

17:24.640 --> 17:26.200
There are only three people in this family,

17:26.230 --> 17:27.800
and you always play the peacemaker,

17:27.819 --> 17:29.290
always acting like the good guy.

17:29.320 --> 17:30.590
What's that saying again?

17:30.700 --> 17:32.190
Is the good guy the red face or the white face?

17:32.500 --> 17:33.350
No idea.

17:33.350 --> 17:34.430
I have no idea.

17:35.220 --> 17:36.700
Whatever it is, you always play the good guy

17:36.700 --> 17:37.780
and leave me to be the bad guy.

17:37.950 --> 17:39.600
I'm the only bad person in this family.

17:39.670 --> 17:41.020
How could Mom be a bad person?

17:41.020 --> 17:41.890
Yeah.

17:41.920 --> 17:43.370
Look, she's so agitated.

17:43.390 --> 17:44.460
It's all the Codonopsis root's fault!

17:44.500 --> 17:46.020
Exactly. From now on,

17:46.020 --> 17:47.540
no more Codonopsis roots in her soup.

17:47.540 --> 17:48.060
Right.

17:48.060 --> 17:49.910
We won't even mention those two words.

17:49.910 --> 17:50.670
Right.

17:50.670 --> 17:52.910
-Don't drink it anymore.
-Not anymore.

17:52.910 --> 17:53.300
Yeah, yeah.

17:53.300 --> 17:53.910
Move it away.

17:53.910 --> 17:54.300
I'll drink it instead.

17:54.300 --> 17:55.700
This soup tastes really good.

17:55.700 --> 17:56.830
You need to learn how to make it

17:56.830 --> 17:58.870
and make it for us often.

17:59.350 --> 18:00.260
You drink some more.

18:00.260 --> 18:01.700
You can't drink it!

18:02.180 --> 18:03.790
It makes you irritable.

18:03.820 --> 18:04.900
You can't drink it!

18:04.920 --> 18:06.190
It's spilled!

18:07.460 --> 18:08.780
Remind the elderly guests

18:08.780 --> 18:09.870
to take all their luggage.

18:09.870 --> 18:11.870
Make sure they check out smoothly.

18:12.780 --> 18:13.500
Alright, that's it.

18:23.540 --> 18:24.120
Madam,

18:24.390 --> 18:25.740
you haven't checked out?

18:26.740 --> 18:27.700
I'm staying a bit longer.

18:28.260 --> 18:29.980
Your hotel is very comfortable,

18:29.980 --> 18:30.940
and the service is great.

18:31.030 --> 18:32.460
I'd like to extend my stay.

18:32.490 --> 18:33.140
Okay.

18:33.350 --> 18:34.540
I'll let the front desk know

18:34.540 --> 18:35.630
and have them arrange your extension.

18:35.900 --> 18:37.340
I'd like to change rooms.

18:38.220 --> 18:40.410
The villas here look really nice.

18:40.510 --> 18:41.700
Can I switch to one of them?

18:41.730 --> 18:43.650
No problem. I'll apply for a discount for you.

18:44.220 --> 18:45.310
That's even better.

18:45.540 --> 18:48.190
Also, could you get me some of that incense from last time?

18:48.190 --> 18:49.060
I really liked it.

18:49.060 --> 18:49.830
Sure thing.

18:50.300 --> 18:51.260
Thank you so much.

18:51.260 --> 18:52.020
You're welcome.

18:52.260 --> 18:52.830
Thanks for your hard work.

18:52.830 --> 18:53.150
Okay.

18:53.150 --> 18:53.830
I'll let you get back to work.

18:54.120 --> 18:55.120
Take care, madam.

18:55.420 --> 18:56.260
Alright, goodbye.

19:01.540 --> 19:02.350
Ms. Shen,

19:02.610 --> 19:04.090
dry your hair before going to bed.

19:04.430 --> 19:05.980
Got it.

19:12.460 --> 19:13.930
I'm so tired.

20:05.690 --> 20:07.900
I slept for 10 hours.

20:10.150 --> 20:11.150
Bliss.

20:14.890 --> 20:15.660
Wait a moment.

20:21.890 --> 20:22.690
It hurts.

20:29.630 --> 20:31.150
Ms. Liu,

20:31.350 --> 20:32.670
Mr. Shen,

20:33.280 --> 20:35.010
help me!

20:36.230 --> 20:39.640
[Honganmen Clinic]

20:49.100 --> 20:50.250
What's wrong with you?

20:50.740 --> 20:52.300
I slept funny last night.

20:52.300 --> 20:54.300
When I woke up, I couldn't move.

20:55.370 --> 20:56.610
A stiff neck, huh?

20:58.630 --> 21:00.360
Alright, let me check on you.

21:03.930 --> 21:04.900
Be gentle, please.

21:04.920 --> 21:07.190
I know. I'm always gentle.

21:21.110 --> 21:21.950
Here?

21:25.870 --> 21:26.700
Relax.

21:39.350 --> 21:40.220
Relax.

21:40.220 --> 21:41.110
It's okay.

21:41.910 --> 21:42.260
It hurts.

21:42.260 --> 21:42.830
How do you feel?

21:42.830 --> 21:44.740
A little better?

21:44.740 --> 21:45.590
Yeah.

21:46.190 --> 21:46.700
Alright.

21:47.500 --> 21:48.020
Here.

21:48.700 --> 21:50.350
Put your chin in my palm.

21:50.690 --> 21:51.340
Relax.

21:52.390 --> 21:54.350
Now, slowly turn your head to the right.

21:56.320 --> 21:57.080
Turn.

21:57.350 --> 21:58.110
Turn.

21:58.300 --> 21:58.950
Turn.

21:59.970 --> 22:00.780
Can you turn any further?

22:00.880 --> 22:01.760
No.

22:02.020 --> 22:02.500
Okay.

22:03.070 --> 22:03.980
Don't strain your neck.

22:09.540 --> 22:10.300
Relax.

22:11.350 --> 22:12.540
Relax.

22:13.190 --> 22:13.690
I...

22:16.330 --> 22:16.960
How is it?

22:17.440 --> 22:18.350
Try moving your neck.

22:19.740 --> 22:20.700
Is it much better?

22:23.670 --> 22:24.460
Much better.

22:25.440 --> 22:26.460
Does it hurt anywhere else?

22:27.390 --> 22:28.540
My back hurts.

22:29.020 --> 22:30.020
Your back hurts too?

22:30.020 --> 22:31.020
Yes, this side.

22:31.500 --> 22:31.980
Alright.

22:32.420 --> 22:33.190
Relax.

22:33.830 --> 22:34.500
Don't move.

22:35.260 --> 22:35.950
Does it hurt here?

22:36.190 --> 22:37.150
It hurts. It hurts.

22:37.910 --> 22:38.500
Here?

22:38.500 --> 22:39.260
A little.

22:39.260 --> 22:40.110
It feels sore.

22:40.550 --> 22:41.620
Alright, get up.

22:42.040 --> 22:43.190
Careful, slow down.

22:44.910 --> 22:45.500
Okay.

22:46.300 --> 22:47.110
Cross your arms

22:47.110 --> 22:48.300
around your shoulders.

22:49.960 --> 22:50.810
Hold tight.

22:50.980 --> 22:51.660
Like this?

22:51.680 --> 22:52.680
Yes, hold tight.

22:59.460 --> 23:00.110
Okay.

23:00.190 --> 23:01.150
Now,

23:01.180 --> 23:02.390
relax slowly

23:02.390 --> 23:03.780
and lean on my shoulder.

23:12.830 --> 23:13.630
Relax.

23:13.980 --> 23:14.780
Relax.

23:29.730 --> 23:30.490
How is it?

23:31.040 --> 23:31.990
How do you feel now?

23:33.350 --> 23:34.350
Much better?

23:37.370 --> 23:38.250
Sit down.

23:42.300 --> 23:44.190
It's important to have a good sleeping posture.

23:44.190 --> 23:45.500
Otherwise, you might get a stiff neck.

23:45.670 --> 23:46.870
I'll prescribe you some medicine.

23:53.150 --> 23:54.260
Here's your prescription.

23:54.260 --> 23:55.700
Take this to get your meds later.

23:56.160 --> 23:57.570
If you're still feeling unwell,

23:57.600 --> 23:58.750
I can get them for you.

24:01.910 --> 24:02.980
Thank you.

24:03.300 --> 24:04.260
What's that face?

24:05.150 --> 24:06.590
I didn't even charge you for the massage.

24:08.180 --> 24:09.310
Thank you so much.

24:10.660 --> 24:11.620
I'm heading out.

24:12.910 --> 24:15.430
Please help me with my meds. Bye-bye.

24:23.070 --> 24:24.350
What's going on?

24:32.870 --> 24:33.870
Hello?

24:34.020 --> 24:35.070
Hey, Xu Xiangya.

24:35.520 --> 24:38.040
You know what? I went to Dr. He for a massage today.

24:38.060 --> 24:39.220
He used so much force

24:39.220 --> 24:40.540
that he literally lifted me off the ground!

24:46.060 --> 24:46.830
Xiangya?

24:51.880 --> 24:53.400
Shen Xifan!

24:53.780 --> 24:55.150
Did you seriously wake me up early

24:55.150 --> 24:56.150
just to tell me

24:56.150 --> 24:57.670
that he's not gentle with women?

25:24.570 --> 25:26.670
[Pharmacy]

25:32.700 --> 25:33.420
Ms. Wu.

25:33.680 --> 25:34.440
Dr. He.

25:34.470 --> 25:36.080
Has Shen Xifan picked up her medicine?

25:36.110 --> 25:37.580
Not yet. Only hers is left.

25:37.610 --> 25:38.500
They're all hers, right?

25:38.910 --> 25:39.740
I'll take them to her.

25:40.350 --> 25:41.670
You'll take them to her?

25:41.670 --> 25:42.870
She lives right across the street.

25:42.870 --> 25:43.950
It's just a few steps away.

25:43.950 --> 25:45.340
Does she really need you to deliver them?

25:46.110 --> 25:46.700
I'm off.

25:47.390 --> 25:48.140
Alright.

26:11.960 --> 26:14.160
Chinese characteristics…

26:19.790 --> 26:21.550
How do I write this?

27:05.180 --> 27:05.940
Shen Xifan.

27:07.150 --> 27:08.110
What a coincidence.

27:08.610 --> 27:09.680
I picked up your medicine.

27:11.090 --> 27:11.850
Thank you.

27:14.150 --> 27:15.020
What's wrong?

27:16.590 --> 27:17.190
Nothing.

27:17.500 --> 27:19.430
I was going to look for you at the clinic.

27:19.870 --> 27:20.630
What for?

27:21.430 --> 27:23.110
I want to ask you about

27:23.110 --> 27:25.390
some professional details on aromatherapy and sachets.

27:26.790 --> 27:28.220
Perfect. Let's talk at my place.

27:33.280 --> 27:33.910
What's wrong?

27:34.350 --> 27:34.940
Let's go.

27:36.950 --> 27:37.700
Okay.

27:38.650 --> 27:39.480
Let me carry this for you.

27:40.670 --> 27:40.980
Thank you.

27:40.980 --> 27:41.500
Let's go.

27:56.380 --> 27:58.730
Come in. Change into these.

27:58.780 --> 27:59.500
Thank you.

28:01.630 --> 28:02.740
I'll put the medicine in the fridge.

28:02.740 --> 28:03.540
Make yourself comfortable.

28:21.840 --> 28:22.560
Have a seat.

28:22.980 --> 28:24.460
I'll get you a drink.

28:24.810 --> 28:25.440
Okay.

28:52.590 --> 28:53.350
Sorry about the mess.

28:53.540 --> 28:54.950
I haven't tidied up in a while.

28:55.120 --> 28:55.850
It's fine.

28:57.590 --> 28:58.350
Why don't you

28:59.060 --> 28:59.780
sit here?

29:00.060 --> 29:00.670
Okay.

29:01.460 --> 29:02.150
Thank you.

29:07.070 --> 29:08.550
So, what do you need me to do?

29:14.220 --> 29:16.740
I want to use this TCM wellness trip

29:16.740 --> 29:18.700
as my practical project

29:18.700 --> 29:20.110
and submit it along with my application

29:20.110 --> 29:21.300
to the school in Switzerland,

29:21.300 --> 29:23.430
but I feel like I still need to polish it up.

29:24.700 --> 29:26.870
How can I help?

29:27.830 --> 29:29.700
I've already finished

29:29.700 --> 29:30.820
the overall project plan,

29:30.850 --> 29:32.520
but I'm still missing an introduction.

29:33.220 --> 29:34.700
Do you have any ideas?

29:34.700 --> 29:35.740
How do you want to write it?

29:37.150 --> 29:40.670
I want to write about the stories behind aromatherapy and sachets

29:40.670 --> 29:42.540
and their historical development.

29:43.540 --> 29:44.740
The earliest records

29:44.740 --> 29:45.950
about sachets

29:45.950 --> 29:48.740
actually date back to the Shang and Zhou dynasties.

29:50.220 --> 29:50.910
I have some materials

29:50.910 --> 29:52.020
that might help.

29:52.610 --> 29:53.480
Wait a moment.

30:02.950 --> 30:04.980
This is an essay I wrote in university

30:04.980 --> 30:06.780
about the culture of sachets.

30:07.700 --> 30:08.870
You can use it as a reference.

30:09.300 --> 30:09.950
Thank you.

30:11.060 --> 30:11.980
Can I take a look?

30:12.190 --> 30:13.110
Of course.

30:31.060 --> 30:34.210
♫A light scent♫

30:38.680 --> 30:42.920
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

30:43.410 --> 30:47.580
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

30:45.560 --> 30:48.110
Do you think I can quote this part?

30:48.260 --> 30:50.460
"Fragrant flowers and herbs

30:48.500 --> 30:55.080
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

30:50.500 --> 30:51.670
were valued by ancient people

30:51.670 --> 30:54.500
over 2,000 years ago as symbols of ritual and sentiment.

30:54.500 --> 30:56.950
The culture of fragrance reached its peak during the Song dynasty."

30:56.450 --> 30:59.340
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

31:02.270 --> 31:06.880
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

31:08.700 --> 31:13.060
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

31:12.830 --> 31:13.980
How does that sound for the part

31:13.660 --> 31:19.050
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

31:13.980 --> 31:14.910
about creative sachets?

31:19.630 --> 31:20.390
Sounds good.

31:22.260 --> 31:23.670
You could also reference the studies of

31:24.060 --> 31:24.670
Hua Tuo,

31:24.910 --> 31:25.780
Sun Simiao,

31:26.020 --> 31:27.740
and Li Shizhen

31:27.740 --> 31:30.260
on the medicinal properties of sachets.

31:30.630 --> 31:31.870
Great idea! That would

31:31.870 --> 31:33.910
tie in even better with the wellness trip theme.

31:34.460 --> 31:36.260
I'll write it here now.

31:36.300 --> 31:37.300
Can you check it for me later?

31:37.470 --> 31:38.430
Sure, no problem.

31:38.660 --> 31:40.790
Do you want to write here or in the study?

31:41.340 --> 31:42.250
Here will do.

31:42.300 --> 31:43.220
Okay.

31:43.220 --> 31:44.930
I'll go do my thing.

31:44.970 --> 31:45.610
Thank you.

32:16.490 --> 32:17.290
Dr. He,

32:18.630 --> 32:19.390
I'm done writing.

32:19.590 --> 32:20.390
Take a look at it.

32:20.670 --> 32:21.350
So quickly?

32:21.930 --> 32:22.410
Let me see.

32:59.700 --> 33:00.540
What's wrong?

33:02.290 --> 33:03.290
I...

33:04.090 --> 33:04.870
I was just thinking

33:04.870 --> 33:06.300
if I didn't write it well,

33:06.300 --> 33:07.190
please don't be too harsh on me.

33:08.310 --> 33:09.660
You are not my student.

33:09.700 --> 33:11.060
Why would I be harsh on you?

33:13.980 --> 33:14.700
Besides,

33:14.910 --> 33:16.740
from what I've read so far, it's really well done.

33:17.650 --> 33:18.340
Really?

33:18.360 --> 33:19.270
Really.

33:23.840 --> 33:24.670
There's no problem with it.

33:26.150 --> 33:28.630
Then, I'll send it to my agent

33:28.630 --> 33:29.590
so he can forward it to the school.

33:29.830 --> 33:30.470
Okay.

33:30.540 --> 33:31.010
Okay.

33:45.170 --> 33:46.010
Your phone's ringing.

33:46.740 --> 33:47.910
It's the overseas education agency.

33:49.070 --> 33:49.940
I'll take it.

33:50.450 --> 33:51.130
Use the study.

33:51.150 --> 33:51.910
It's quiet there.

33:52.280 --> 33:52.800
Okay.

33:52.830 --> 33:53.490
I'll be back soon.

33:55.430 --> 33:56.270
Hello?

33:58.200 --> 34:00.200
Is there a problem with the application materials?

34:04.030 --> 34:04.920
Go ahead.

35:27.890 --> 35:32.130
♫Two little hearts♫

35:32.710 --> 35:37.480
♫Found each other♫

35:41.190 --> 35:45.420
♫Never apart♫

35:45.920 --> 35:50.520
♫Sticking together♫

35:54.040 --> 35:58.940
♫You and I♫

36:00.520 --> 36:05.200
♫Side by side by side♫

36:07.190 --> 36:11.950
♫You and I♫

36:12.800 --> 36:15.100
♫Tonight♫

36:18.410 --> 36:24.210
♫And we go lalala♫

36:32.060 --> 36:32.700
Coming.

36:56.660 --> 36:57.950
Manager Shen?

36:58.220 --> 36:59.340
What are you doing here?

37:01.100 --> 37:02.310
I'm here to discuss something

37:02.800 --> 37:03.820
with Dr. He.

37:08.500 --> 37:10.090
I didn't interrupt anything, did I?

37:10.120 --> 37:10.960
No.

37:10.980 --> 37:11.830
Not at all.

37:18.870 --> 37:19.790
Why are you here?

37:19.810 --> 37:20.580
I'm meeting

37:20.580 --> 37:22.710
Professor Yu tomorrow to discuss my research report.

37:23.230 --> 37:25.580
I brought it over for you to check it for me first.

37:26.890 --> 37:28.400
I brought some food too.

37:31.300 --> 37:33.800
Since you two have serious business to handle,

37:33.820 --> 37:35.270
I'll get going.

37:35.450 --> 37:37.010
I'm done with my thing anyway.

37:38.600 --> 37:40.510
I'll get your medicine for you.

37:41.310 --> 37:42.100
Your glasses.

38:06.350 --> 38:07.020
Your medicine.

38:10.220 --> 38:10.700
Well,

38:10.840 --> 38:11.460
thank you.

38:13.520 --> 38:14.120
I'll leave you two to it.

38:15.130 --> 38:15.740
Bye-bye.

38:27.900 --> 38:29.010
You're working hard tonight.

38:29.390 --> 38:30.390
Is that a bad thing?

38:30.700 --> 38:31.660
Working hard

38:32.670 --> 38:33.540
is good.

38:33.970 --> 38:35.380
But tonight isn't the best time.

38:35.650 --> 38:36.650
Tonight?

38:40.830 --> 38:43.190
You like Manager Shen, don't you?

38:47.670 --> 38:49.050
I knew it.

38:49.080 --> 38:50.730
Last time at the hotel,

38:50.790 --> 38:53.460
there were sparks between the two of you.

38:53.500 --> 38:54.460
What stage are you at now?

38:54.460 --> 38:55.430
Tell me!

38:56.010 --> 38:57.010
How is that any of your business?

38:57.030 --> 38:57.720
You talk too much.
